title: Estádio Municipal do Dande
text:
Estádio Municipal do Dande is a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Caxito">Caxito</a>, the capital city of <a href="Angola">Angola</a>'s <a href="Bengo%20Province">Bengo Province</a>. It is the current home stadium of first division side <a href="Domant%20FC">Domant FC</a>. The stadium holds 4,700.
Upon inauguration in 2015, the stadium became the home ground of local club <a href="Domant%20FC">Domant FC</a>.
